標準ライブラリを使う

find_closest_elements = 入力 numbers に対し {
    sorted_numbers = numbers を ソートする
    closest_a = sorted_numbers[0]
    closest_b = sorted_numbers[1]
    min_diff = closest_b - closest_a

    1 から (sorted_numbers の長さ - 2) まで 繰り返す i について {
        a = sorted_numbers[i]
        b = sorted_numbers[i + 1]
        diff = b - a

        もし diff < min_diff なら {
            min_diff = diff
            closest_a = a
            closest_b = b
        }
    }

    (closest_a, closest_b)
}